Stealing the Magic Orb from the Orcs
The Orc Seer keeps the Magic Orb on an altar located on one of the islands. The Seer's bodyguards are always on the island. 
Note: You can reach the islands only by means of the drawbridge. To lower the bridge you must possess the island Orcs' mechanism.
#subobj  1
Find the altar
The altar is located on the southernmost island. On the way there, avoid the central and eastern islands: no need to take unnecessary risks.
#subobj  2
Take the orb
To get the orb you must first kill the guards!
